arcade.gui

Class ARCADE

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.gui.ARCADE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class ARCADE
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    Creates a GUI for selecting setup file and running the simulation.

    When the model is called with arguments, then the main method in Main is called directly and the GUI is not shown.

    Since:
    2.3
    Version:
    2.3.1
